data.title: Lillian Massey and John Treble - Marriage Records
data.meta_description: Ancestry.ca has at least 1 marriage record for Lillian Massey and John Treble, among more than 305 marriage records for the surname Massey and more than 47 marriage records for the surname Treble.
data.text:
Ancestry.ca, the largest online family history resource, can help you explore marriage records for Lillian Massey and John Treble from among its billions of historical records from Canada and around the world.

Marriage records are primary resources for the marriage details, since they were created at the time of the marriage. Ancestry.ca collections include indexes that can help you request the record, and in some cases, actual images of the marriage records.
